rgin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">14.swapcase(self):对字符串的大小写字母进行转换</strong></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;string&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;This&nbsp;IS&nbsp;a&nbsp;String&#39;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;string.swapcase()\r\n&#39;tHIS&nbsp;is&nbsp;A&nbsp;sTRING&#39;</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">15.startswith(str, beg=0, end=len(string))<strong style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">:<strong style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">判断是否以某字符开始</strong></strong></strong></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;string&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;string.&#39;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;string.startswith(&#39;this&#39;)\r\nTrue\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;string.startswith(&#39;xx&#39;)\r\nFalse</pre>','2017-05-11 18:01:02.888077',0,1,1),
	(14,'Django项目常用验证及写法','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Django项目中常用的验证写法</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">命名python文件，如：validate.py，加入类似如下内容（具体自己用到的验证自己写）：</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">#&nbsp;coding:utf-8\r\n\r\nimport&nbsp;re\r\nimport&nbsp;json\r\nfrom&nbsp;urlparse&nbsp;import&nbsp;urlparse\r\n&nbsp;\r\nclass&nbsp;IpValidate(object):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;ip_validate(self,&nbsp;ip):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;parts&nbsp;=&nbsp;ip.split(&quot;.&quot;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;len(parts)&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;4:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False,&nbsp;&quot;IP&nbsp;is&nbsp;invalidate&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;len(parts)&nbsp;==&nbsp;4:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;part&nbsp;in&nbsp;parts:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;str(part).isdigit():\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;int(part)&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;0&nbsp;or&nbsp;int(part)&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;255:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False,&nbsp;&quot;IP&nbsp;is&nbsp;invalidate&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False,&nbsp;&quot;IP&nbsp;is&nbsp;invalidate1&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True,&nbsp;&quot;&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nclass&nbsp;EmailValidate(object):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;__init__(self,&nbsp;email):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.email&nbsp;=&nbsp;email\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;email_validate(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;email&nbsp;=&nbsp;self.email\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;reg&nbsp;=&nbsp;re.compile(&quot;^.+\\\\@(\\\\[?)[a-zA-Z0-9\\\\-\\\\.]+\\\\.([a-zA-Z]{2,3}|[0-9]{1,3})(\\\\]?)$&quot;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;success&nbsp;=&nbsp;reg.match(email)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;success:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False,&nbsp;&#39;Email不合法&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True,&nbsp;&#39;&#39;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nclass&nbsp;ChannelUpdateValidate(IpValidate,&nbsp;EmailValidate):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;VALIDATORS&nbsp;=&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_ip&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_port&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_origin_url&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;run_validators(self,&nbsp;validators):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;validator&nbsp;in&nbsp;validators:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;hasattr(self,&nbsp;validator):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;func&nbsp;=&nbsp;getattr(self,&nbsp;validator)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;func():\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_params(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;self.run_validators(self.VALIDATORS)\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;__init__(self,&nbsp;ip,&nbsp;port,&nbsp;origin_url):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.ip&nbsp;=&nbsp;ip\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.port&nbsp;=&nbsp;port\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.origin_url&nbsp;=&nbsp;origin_url\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_ip(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ips&nbsp;=&nbsp;self.ip.split(&quot;,&quot;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;ip&nbsp;in&nbsp;ips:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ip_success,&nbsp;message&nbsp;=&nbsp;self.ip_validate(ip)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;domain_success,&nbsp;message&nbsp;=&nbsp;self.domain_validate(ip)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;ip_success&nbsp;and&nbsp;not&nbsp;domain_success:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;源站不合法&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True,&nbsp;&quot;&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_port(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;str(self.port).isdigit():\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True,&nbsp;&quot;&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;端口号不合法&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_origin_url(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;reg&nbsp;=&nbsp;re.compile(&quot;^(?:http|ftp)?://&quot;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;success&nbsp;=&nbsp;reg.match(self.origin_url)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;success:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;URL格式错误&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True,&nbsp;&#39;&#39;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nclass&nbsp;ChannelValidate(ChannelUpdateValidate):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;VALIDATORS&nbsp;=&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_domain&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_ip&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_port&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_origin_url&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;__init__(self,&nbsp;ip,&nbsp;port,&nbsp;origin_url,&nbsp;domain):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.ip&nbsp;=&nbsp;ip\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.domain&nbsp;=&nbsp;domain\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.port&nbsp;=&nbsp;port\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.origin_url&nbsp;=&nbsp;origin_url\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_domain(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;success,&nbsp;message&nbsp;=&nbsp;self.domain_validate(self.domain)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;success:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;域名不合法&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True,&nbsp;&quot;&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nclass&nbsp;UserValidate(EmailValidate):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;VALIDATORS&nbsp;=&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_email&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;validate_phone&quot;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;run_validators(self,&nbsp;validators):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;validator&nbsp;in&nbsp;validators:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;hasattr(self,&nbsp;validator):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;func&nbsp;=&nbsp;getattr(self,&nbsp;validator)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;func():\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_params(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;self.run_validators(self.VALIDATORS)\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;__init__(self,&nbsp;email,&nbsp;phone):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.email&nbsp;=&nbsp;email\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.phone&nbsp;=&nbsp;phone\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_email(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;success,&nbsp;message&nbsp;=&nbsp;self.email_validate()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;success:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;message\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;validate_phone(self):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;phone&nbsp;=&nbsp;self.phone\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;str(phone).isdigit():\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;电话号码不合法&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;reg&nbsp;=&nbsp;re.compile(&quot;^[0-9]{7,12}$&quot;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;success&nbsp;=&nbsp;reg.match(phone)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;success:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.message&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;电话号码不合法&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;False\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;True</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">用法：&nbsp;在需要验证的python文件中导入validate.py，然后类似如下代码：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;create_user(request):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;params&nbsp;=&nbsp;request.POST\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;user&nbsp;=&nbsp;User.objects.filter(email=params[&#39;email&#39;])\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;validate_user&nbsp;=&nbsp;UserValidate(params[&quot;email&quot;],&nbsp;params[&quot;mobile_phone&quot;])\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;success&nbsp;=&nbsp;validate_user.validate_params()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;not&nbsp;success:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;render_json({&#39;success&#39;:&nbsp;False,&nbsp;&#39;message&#39;:&nbsp;validate_user.message})\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;user.count()&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;0:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;render_json({&#39;success&#39;:&nbsp;False,&nbsp;&#39;message&#39;:&nbsp;u&#39;用户已存在！&#39;})\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;User.add(params[&#39;email&#39;],&nbsp;params[&#39;password&#39;],&nbsp;params[&#39;contact&#39;],&nbsp;params[&#39;mobile_phone&#39;],&nbsp;params[&#39;role&#39;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;params[&#39;comments&#39;])\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;render_json({&#39;success&#39;:&nbsp;True,&nbsp;&#39;message&#39;:&nbsp;u&#39;添加成功！&#39;})</pre>','2017-08-23 18:28:43.496799',0,1,8),
	(15,'Python + Django项目常用装饰器及自定义函数','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.自定义返回请求值的函数：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;render_json(data,&nbsp;status=200):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;HttpResponse(json.dumps(data),&nbsp;content_type=&quot;text/json&quot;,&nbsp;status=status)\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;render_json_error(message,&nbsp;status=400):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;render_json(message,&nbsp;status)\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;response_401(msg=&quot;Unauthorized&quot;):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;HttpResponse(msg&nbsp;+&nbsp;&quot;\\n&quot;,&nbsp;status=401)\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;response_400(msg=&quot;Bad&nbsp;Request&quot;):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;HttpResponse(msg&nbsp;+&nbsp;&quot;\\n&quot;,&nbsp;status=400)\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;response_403(msg=&quot;Forbidden&quot;):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;HttpResponse(msg&nbsp;+&nbsp;&quot;\\n&quot;,&nbsp;status=403)\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;response_404(msg=&quot;Not&nbsp;Found&quot;):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;HttpResponse(msg&nbsp;+&nbsp;&quot;\\n&quot;,&nbsp;status=404)\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;response_200(msg=&quot;OK&quot;):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;HttpResponse(msg&nbsp;+&nbsp;&quot;\\n&quot;,&nbsp;status=200)</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.自定义格式化时间的函数：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;format_time(date):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;date.strftime(&quot;%Y-%m-%d&nbsp;%H:%M&quot;)</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.操作日志装饰器：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;log_action(action,&nbsp;method=&quot;ALL&quot;):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;log_action_wrapper(func):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@wraps(func)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;_wrapper(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;method&nbsp;==&nbsp;&quot;ALL&quot;&nbsp;or&nbsp;request.method&nbsp;==&nbsp;method:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;user&nbsp;=&nbsp;request.user\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ActionLog.add(action,&nbsp;user.name)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;func(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;_wrapper\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;log_action_wrapper</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.权限需求装饰器：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;admin_required(func):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@wraps(func)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;_wrapper(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;role&nbsp;=&nbsp;request.session[&#39;role&#39;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;role&nbsp;==&nbsp;USER_ROLE[0]:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;render_json({&#39;success&#39;:&nbsp;False,&nbsp;&#39;message&#39;:&nbsp;_(&#39;Sorry,&nbsp;you&nbsp;have&nbsp;no&nbsp;permission&#39;)})\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;func(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;_wrapper</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.要求登录装饰器：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;login_require(func):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@wraps(func)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;_wrapper(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;&#39;user_id&#39;&nbsp;not&nbsp;in&nbsp;request.session:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;request.user&nbsp;=&nbsp;None\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;render(request,&nbsp;&#39;portal/login/login.html&#39;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;func(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;_wrapper</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6.导航栏选中变亮装饰器：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;active_navs(*nav_args):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;active_navs_wrapper(func):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@wraps(func)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;_wrapper(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;request.actives&nbsp;=&nbsp;nav_args\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;func(request,&nbsp;*args,&nbsp;**kwargs)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;_wrapper\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;active_navs_wrapper</pre>','2017-05-11 18:33:37.329775',0,1,1),
	(16,'Ubuntu修改gem源','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 大家都在国内，所以访问gem的国外官网很痛苦，在用gem安装软件的时候，很可能安装不上，幸好淘宝为大家做了一个镜像，每15分钟同步一次国外的官网，所以，可以把gem源换为淘宝源。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">淘宝网提供了Rubygems的国内镜像站：https://ruby.taobao.org/</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.先使用命令查看一下，现有源地址：</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">～$&nbsp;gem&nbsp;souce\r\nhttp://rubygems.org/</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.删除原有源：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">gem&nbsp;source&nbsp;-r&nbsp;http://rubygems.org/</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.添加淘宝的gem源：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">gem&nbsp;source&nbsp;-a&nbsp;https://ruby.taobao.org/</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.更新缓存：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">gem&nbsp;sources&nbsp;-u</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">好了，接下来就可以愉快地用gem安装软件了</span></p>','2016-08-11 18:39:46.908694',0,1,9),
	(17,'Ubuntu上安装与设置ssh，实现无密码登录','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SSH为Secure Shell 的缩写，是目前较可靠，专为远程登录会话和其他网络服务提供安全性的协议。越来越多的小伙伴们使用远程登录，而ssh安全性无疑是很高的，那么我们现在来看看如何安装ssh服务器，实现无密码登录。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.首先要安装ssh，终端中执行:</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">ssh-keygen</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">之后连敲三次回车即可。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.完成过后，可以查看到用户主目录下.ssh文件夹下多了id_rsa(私钥)和id_rsa.pub(公钥)两个文件，一个是存储公钥的文件，另一个是存储私钥的文件。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.使用</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">cat&nbsp;~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub&nbsp;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;~/.ssh/authorized_keys</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">命令（注意是两个大于号，一个大于号是覆盖文件，两个大于号是累加内容）将id_rsa.pub(公钥)文件中的内容累加写入到~/.ssh/authorized_keys(已认证)文件中。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.要无密码登录其他电脑，只需要将authorized_keys文件放置到其他机子的~/.ssh/目录下（前提是其他电脑也安装了ssh服务）。可以通过scp传输，如下所示，scp后面接要传输的文件名 然后接其他电脑的用户名@IP:传输的目录。</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">scp&nbsp;~/.ssh/authorized_keys&nbsp;root@172.168.11.00:~/.ssh/</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.然后，命令行输入ssh 后面接其他电脑用户名@IP，就会发现无密码就可登录其他电脑。(如果需要双向无密码登录，同理只要让另一台电脑生成密钥，把公钥内容累加到这台电脑的authorized_keys中即可。)</span></p>','2016-08-26 18:43:14.475770',0,1,11),
	(18,'Ubuntu 14.04上使用Gunicorn，Nginx，Capistrano一键部署django项目','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Gunicorn 绿色独角兽是一个Python WSGI UNIX的HTTP服务器。这是一个pre-fork worker的模型，从Ruby的独角兽（<a href=\"http://www.oschina.net/p/unicorn\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 133, 197); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Unicorn</a>&nbsp;）项目移植。该Gunicorn服务器大致与各种Web框架兼容，只需非常简单的执行，轻量级的资源消耗，以及相当迅速。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">特点：<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 本身支持WSGI、Django、Paster<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 自动辅助进程管理<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 简单的 Python配置<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 允许配置多个工作环境<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 各种服务器的可扩展钩子<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 与Python 2.x &gt; = 2.5 兼容</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.首先在你的本地电脑上安装capistrano</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;capistrano</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">也可以用gem安装capistrano(参考修改gem源和修改ruby默认版本两篇博文)</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">gem&nbsp;install&nbsp;capistrano</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.然后在你的Django项目目录下运行</span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">cap&nbsp;install</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后会生成Capfile和config文件夹，config文件夹下有deploy文件夹和deploy.rb文件等。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.编辑deploy文件夹下的production.rb文件如下：</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">set&nbsp;:deploy_to,&nbsp;&quot;/root/#{fetch&nbsp;:application}&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;#&nbsp;部署的位置，此处在/root/下\r\nset&nbsp;:branch,&nbsp;&#39;develop&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#&nbsp;要部署的分支名\r\n&nbsp;\r\nserver&nbsp;&#39;172.16.254.20&#39;,&nbsp;roles:&nbsp;[:web,&nbsp;:db]&nbsp;&nbsp;#&nbsp;服务器的地址，操作的对象是服务器和数据库</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.编辑config文件夹下的deploy.rb文件如下：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">set&nbsp;:application,&nbsp;&#39;my_site&#39;\r\nset&nbsp;:repo_url,&nbsp;&#39;git@github.com:a1401358759/my_site.git&#39;\r\nset&nbsp;:ssh_options,&nbsp;{user:&nbsp;&#39;root&#39;}\r\nset&nbsp;:scm,&nbsp;:git\r\nset&nbsp;:keep_releases,&nbsp;5\r\nset&nbsp;:stages,&nbsp;%w(master&nbsp;staging&nbsp;production)\r\nset&nbsp;:default_stage,&nbsp;&quot;master&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nnamespace&nbsp;:deploy&nbsp;do\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;after&nbsp;:updated,&nbsp;:config_files&nbsp;do\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;on&nbsp;roles(:all)&nbsp;do\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;execute&nbsp;&quot;ln&nbsp;-s&nbsp;#{fetch&nbsp;:deploy_to}/shared/log&nbsp;#{fetch&nbsp;:release_path}/log&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;execute&nbsp;&quot;cp&nbsp;/root/my_site-config/config.py&nbsp;#{fetch&nbsp;:release_path}/my_site/&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;execute&nbsp;&quot;cp&nbsp;/root/my_site-config/gunicorn.conf&nbsp;#{fetch&nbsp;:release_path}&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;end\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;end\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;after&nbsp;:published,&nbsp;:restart_web&nbsp;do\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;on&nbsp;roles(:web)&nbsp;do\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;within&nbsp;&quot;#{fetch&nbsp;:deploy_to}/current&quot;&nbsp;do\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;execute&nbsp;:bash,&nbsp;&quot;runserver.sh&nbsp;restart-web&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;end\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;end\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;end\r\nend</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.在项目目录下新建runserver.sh文件，内容如下：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">#!&nbsp;/bin/sh\r\nBASE_DIR=`dirname&nbsp;$0`\r\nWORK_DIR=`pwd`/$BASE_DIR\r\nLOG_DIR=$BASE_DIR/log\r\nGUNICORN_PID_FILE=`pwd`/$LOG_DIR/gunicorn.pid\r\nSCRIPT_NAME=runserver.sh\r\nPYTHON_PATH=`which&nbsp;python`\r\nINI_FILE=$WORK_DIR/gunicorn.conf\r\n&nbsp;\r\nstart_web()&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;Start&nbsp;Gunicorn&nbsp;Server\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;gunicorn&nbsp;-c&nbsp;$INI_FILE&nbsp;my_site.wsgi:application\r\n}\r\n&nbsp;\r\nstop_web()&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;[&nbsp;-f&nbsp;$GUNICORN_PID_FILE&nbsp;];&nbsp;then\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;Stop&nbsp;Gunicorn&nbsp;Server\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;pid&nbsp;in&nbsp;`cat&nbsp;$GUNICORN_PID_FILE`\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;do\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;kill&nbsp;$pid\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;done\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rm&nbsp;-f&nbsp;$GUNICORN_PID_FILE\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fi\r\n}\r\n&nbsp;\r\nreload_web()&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;[&nbsp;-f&nbsp;$GUNICORN_PID_FILE&nbsp;];&nbsp;then\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;Reload&nbsp;Gunicorn&nbsp;Server\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;kill&nbsp;-HUP&nbsp;`cat&nbsp;$GUNICORN_PID_FILE`\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;start_web\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fi\r\n}\r\n&nbsp;\r\ncase&nbsp;$1&nbsp;in\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;start-web):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;start_web\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;stop-web)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;stop_web\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;restart-web)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;reload_web\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;Usage:&nbsp;$SCRIPT_NAME&nbsp;(\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;start-web|stop-web|restart-web\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)&quot;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;;;\r\nesac</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6.在服务器上安装基本软件环境：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;git\r\nsudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;ruby\r\nsudo&nbsp;gem&nbsp;install&nbsp;capistrano(sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;capistrano)\r\nsudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;mysql-server&nbsp;mysql-client\r\nsudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;python-pip&nbsp;python-dev\r\nsudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;--upgrade&nbsp;pip\r\nsudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;django==1.8.7\r\nsudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;MySQL-python\r\nsudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;openjdk-7-jdk\r\nsudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;python-mysqldb\r\nsudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;django-mysqlpool\r\nsudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;nginx-full\r\nsudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;gunicorn</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">7.在/root/下创建portal-config文件夹：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">cd&nbsp;/root/mkdir&nbsp;portal-config</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">8.在portal-config文件夹下创建config.py和gunicorn.conf文件：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">config.py内容如下：</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">DEBUG&nbsp;=&nbsp;True\r\n&nbsp;\r\nRUNNING_ENVIRONMENT&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;Develop&#39;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nSITE_DOMAIN&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;http://127.0.0.1:8000&quot;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nDATABASE&nbsp;=&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;database&#39;:&nbsp;&#39;&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;host&#39;:&nbsp;&#39;127.0.0.1&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;username&#39;:&nbsp;&#39;root&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;password&#39;:&nbsp;&#39;&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;port&#39;:&nbsp;3306,\r\n}\r\n&nbsp;\r\nEMAIL&nbsp;=&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;host&#39;:&nbsp;&#39;&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;user&#39;:&nbsp;&#39;&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;password&#39;:&nbsp;&#39;&#39;\r\n}</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">gunicorn.conf内容如下：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">bind&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;127.0.0.1:9002&#39;\r\nproc_name&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;portal.proc&#39;\r\nchdir=&nbsp;&#39;/root/portal/current&#39;\r\nworkers&nbsp;=&nbsp;4\r\ndaemon&nbsp;=&nbsp;True\r\nloglevel&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;info&#39;\r\npidfile&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;/root/portal/current/log/gunicorn.pid&#39;\r\nlogfile&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;/root/portal/current/log/gunicorn-production.log&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;//以上portal均为项目名称</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">9.新建项目nginx配置文件portal.conf：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">cd&nbsp;/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/\r\nrm&nbsp;-rf&nbsp;default\r\ntouch&nbsp;portal.conf</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">portal.conf文件的内容如下：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">server&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;listen&nbsp;80;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;index&nbsp;index.html&nbsp;index.htm;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;server_name&nbsp;localhost;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;location&nbsp;~&nbsp;^/static&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;root&nbsp;/root/portal/current/;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;location&nbsp;~&nbsp;^/admin{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;root&nbsp;/root/portal/current/static;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;include&nbsp;uwsgi_params;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;proxy_pass&nbsp;http://127.0.0.1:9002;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//此处为gunicorn.conf中的bind的值\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.重启nginx服务和启动gunicorn服务：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">service&nbsp;nginx&nbsp;restart\r\ncd&nbsp;/root/portal/\r\n./runserver.sh&nbsp;start-web</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">11.最后到本地的项目目录下执行如下命令：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">cap&nbsp;production&nbsp;deploy&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#&nbsp;一键部署</pre>','2016-10-08 18:52:34.433259',0,1,7),
	(19,'Ubuntu系统常用环境安装','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.系统更新，以便和最新的软件兼容：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;update</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.安装Git：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;git</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.安装Ruby环境：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;ruby\r\n~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;gem&nbsp;install&nbsp;capistrano</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.安装Mysql：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;mysql-server&nbsp;mysql-client</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">5.安装python环境：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (1) 安装pip命令：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;python-pip&nbsp;python-dev\r\n~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;--upgrade&nbsp;pip</pre><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(2) 安装Django：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;django==1.8.7</pre><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (3) 安装Mysql库：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;MySQL-python</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6.安装java环境:</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;openjdk-7-jdk</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">7.生成SSH Key：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;ssh-keygen&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#&nbsp;连续敲三次回车\r\n~$&nbsp;cat&nbsp;~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub&nbsp;&nbsp;#&nbsp;查看生成的公钥</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">8.安装memcached包：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;python-memcached</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">9.安装Mysql连接池：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;python-mysqldb\r\n~$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;django-mysqlpool</pre>','2016-11-11 18:59:18.169557',0,1,12),
	(20,'Python的特性','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 这篇文章的目的就是想整理一些Python的高级特性，试图为大家揭开Python的神秘面纱。Python的高级特性如果深入写的话可以写成一本书，所以这篇文章也只是浅尝辄止。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">1.匿名函数lambda(是指一类无需定义标识符（函数名）的函数或子程序):</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">使用lambda可以定义简单的单行匿名函数。如：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">fib&nbsp;=&nbsp;lambda&nbsp;n:&nbsp;n&nbsp;if&nbsp;n&lt;=2&nbsp;else&nbsp;fib(n-1)&nbsp;+&nbsp;fib(n-2)\r\nlambda_add&nbsp;=&nbsp;lambda&nbsp;x,&nbsp;y:&nbsp;x&nbsp;+&nbsp;y</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">2.将函数作为参数传递:</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;在Python中可将函数作为参数传递。其原因就在于函数也是对象。实际上，在 Python 中函数是一级对象。你可以像其他对象一样使用而没有什么特别的限制。关于函数就是对象的一个最常见的例子就是 C 中的函数指针；将函数传递到其他的将要使用它的函数。</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;def&nbsp;greeter():\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print&nbsp;&#39;hello&nbsp;world&#39;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;def&nbsp;repeat(fn,&nbsp;times):\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;i&nbsp;in&nbsp;xrange(times):\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fn()\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;repeat(greeter,&nbsp;3)\r\nhello&nbsp;world\r\nhello&nbsp;world\r\nhello&nbsp;world</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">3.闭包:</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;如果在一个内部函数里，对在外部作用域（但不是在全局作用域）的变量进行引用，那么内部函数就被认为是闭包（closure）。其实最准确的说法应该是闭包是由函数和与其相关的引用环境组合而成的实体。如：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;a&nbsp;=&nbsp;0\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;def&nbsp;get_a():\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;a\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;get_a()\r\n0\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;a&nbsp;=&nbsp;3\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;get_a()\r\n3</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">上述例子中，a为一个global变量，a和get_a()组成了一个闭包，所以a改变时也会直接反应到get_a()函数中。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">作用：闭包的作用不言而喻，加强模块化，增强抽象等等。而且在闭包的基础上才实现了装饰器。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">4.装饰器:</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;装饰器是一个很著名的设计模式，经常被用于有切面需求的场景，较为经典的有插入日志、性能测试、事务处理等。装饰器是解决这类问题的绝佳设计，有了装饰器，我们就可以抽离出大量函数中与函数功能本身无关的雷同代码并继续重用。概括的讲，装饰器的作用就是为已经存在的对象添加额外的功能。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">比如你想在在调用某个函数时都想计算其执行时间，那么就可以使用装饰器来进行，比如下面的代码：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;def&nbsp;time_use(func):\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def&nbsp;wrapper():\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;start&nbsp;=&nbsp;time.clock()\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;func()\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;end&nbsp;=&nbsp;time.clock()\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print&nbsp;&#39;used:&#39;,&nbsp;end&nbsp;-&nbsp;start\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;wrapper\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;@time_use\r\n...&nbsp;def&nbsp;foo():\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print&nbsp;&#39;hello&nbsp;world&#39;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;foo()\r\nhello&nbsp;world\r\nused:&nbsp;0.000116</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">5.生成器(只能使用一次)</strong>:</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;通过列表生成式，我们可以直接创建一个列表。但是，受到内存限制，列表容量肯定是有限的。而且，创建一个包含100万个元素的列表，不仅占用很大的存储空间，如果我们仅仅需要访问前面几个元素，那后面绝大多数元素占用的空间都白白浪费了。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;所以，如果列表元素可以按照某种算法推算出来，那我们是否可以在循环的过程中不断推算出后续的元素呢？这样就不必创建完整的list，从而节省大量的空间。在Python中，这种一边循环一边计算的机制，称为生成器（Generator）。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;要创建一个generator，有很多种方法。第一种方法很简单，只要把一个列表生成式的<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">[]</code>改成<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">()</code>，就创建了一个generator：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;L&nbsp;=&nbsp;[x&nbsp;*&nbsp;x&nbsp;for&nbsp;x&nbsp;in&nbsp;range(10)]\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;L\r\n[0,&nbsp;1,&nbsp;4,&nbsp;9,&nbsp;16,&nbsp;25,&nbsp;36,&nbsp;49,&nbsp;64,&nbsp;81]\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g&nbsp;=&nbsp;(x&nbsp;*&nbsp;x&nbsp;for&nbsp;x&nbsp;in&nbsp;range(10))\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g\r\n&lt;generator&nbsp;object&nbsp;&lt;genexpr&gt;&nbsp;at&nbsp;0x104feab40&gt;</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">创建<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">L</code>和<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">g</code>的区别仅在于最外层的<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">[]</code>和<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">()</code>，<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">L</code>是一个list，而<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">g</code>是一个generator。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">我们可以直接打印出list的每一个元素，但我们怎么打印出generator的每一个元素呢？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">如果要一个一个打印出来，可以通过generator的<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">next()</code>方法：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n0\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n1\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n4\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n9\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n16\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n25\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n36\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n49\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n64\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\n81\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g.next()\r\nTraceback&nbsp;(most&nbsp;recent&nbsp;call&nbsp;last):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;File&nbsp;&quot;&lt;stdin&gt;&quot;,&nbsp;line&nbsp;1,&nbsp;in&nbsp;&lt;module&gt;\r\nStopIteration</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">generator保存的是算法，每次调用<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">next()</code>，就计算出下一个元素的值，直到计算到最后一个元素，没有更多的元素时，抛出StopIteration的错误。当然，上面这种不断调用<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">next()</code>方法实在太变态了，正确的方法是使用<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">for</code>循环，因为generator也是可迭代对象：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;g&nbsp;=&nbsp;(x&nbsp;*&nbsp;x&nbsp;for&nbsp;x&nbsp;in&nbsp;range(10))\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;for&nbsp;n&nbsp;in&nbsp;g:\r\n...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print&nbsp;n\r\n...\r\n0\r\n1\r\n4\r\n9\r\n16\r\n25\r\n36\r\n49\r\n64\r\n81</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">比如用函数的方法来实现斐波那契数列：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;fib(max):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;n,&nbsp;a,&nbsp;b&nbsp;=&nbsp;0,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;1\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;n&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;max:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print&nbsp;b\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a,&nbsp;b&nbsp;=&nbsp;b,&nbsp;a&nbsp;+&nbsp;b\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;n&nbsp;=&nbsp;n&nbsp;+&nbsp;1\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;fib(n):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;n&nbsp;&lt;=&nbsp;2:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;esle:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;fib(n-1)&nbsp;+&nbsp;fib(n-2)\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\ndef&nbsp;fib(n):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a,&nbsp;b&nbsp;=&nbsp;0,&nbsp;1\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;i&nbsp;in&nbsp;xrange(n):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a,&nbsp;b&nbsp;=&nbsp;b,&nbsp;a&nbsp;+&nbsp;b\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;b</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上面的函数会输出前n个数：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;fib(5)\r\n1\r\n1\r\n2\r\n3\r\n5</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">仔细观察，可以看出，<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">fib</code>函数实际上是定义了斐波拉契数列的推算规则，可以从第一个元素开始，推算出后续任意的元素，这种逻辑其实非常类似generator。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">也就是说，上面的函数和generator仅一步之遥。要把<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">fib</code>函数变成generator，只需要把<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">print b</code>改为<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">yield b</code>就可以了：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">def&nbsp;fib(max):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;n,&nbsp;a,&nbsp;b&nbsp;=&nbsp;0,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;1\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;n&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;max:\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;yield&nbsp;b\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a,&nbsp;b&nbsp;=&nbsp;b,&nbsp;a&nbsp;+&nbsp;b\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;n&nbsp;=&nbsp;n&nbsp;+&nbsp;1</pre><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这就是定义generator的另一种方法。如果一个函数定义中包含</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal;\">yield</code><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关键字，那么这个函数就不再是一个普通函数，而是一个generator：</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;fib(6)\r\n&lt;generator&nbsp;object&nbsp;fib&nbsp;at&nbsp;0x104feaaa0&gt;</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 这里，最难理解的就是generator和函数的执行流程不一样。函数是顺序执行，遇到return语句或者最后一行函数语句就返回。而变成generator的函数，在每次调用<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">next()</code>的时候执行，遇到<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">yield</code>语句返回，再次执行时从上次返回的<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">yield</code>语句处继续执行。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">6.迭代器:</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 10px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;可以直接作用于for循环的对象叫可迭代对象，可以被next()函数调用并不断返回容器中下一个值的对象叫迭代器。迭代器有两个方法：next()返回容器中的下一个元素；__iter__返回迭代器对象本身。如：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;l&nbsp;=&nbsp;[1,2]\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;it&nbsp;=&nbsp;iter(l)\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;print&nbsp;it\r\n&lt;listiterator&nbsp;object&nbsp;at&nbsp;0x108033990&gt;\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;print&nbsp;it.next()\r\n1\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;print&nbsp;it.next()\r\n2\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;print&nbsp;it.next()\r\nTraceback&nbsp;(most&nbsp;recent&nbsp;call&nbsp;last):\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;File&nbsp;&quot;&lt;stdin&gt;&quot;,&nbsp;line&nbsp;1,&nbsp;in&nbsp;&lt;module&gt;\r\nStopIteration</pre>','2016-12-16 19:05:49.386947',0,1,1),
	(21,'Python 虚拟环境：Virtualenv','<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Oxygen, Georgia, serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(82, 82, 82); margin: 1.25rem 0px; font-size: 1.4em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">virtualenv</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">virtualenv用于创建独立的Python环境，多个Python相互独立，互不影响，它能够：</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">1. 在没有权限的情况下安装新套件</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">2. 不同应用可以使用不同的套件版本</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">3. 套件升级不影响其他应用</span></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Oxygen, Georgia, serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(82, 82, 82); margin: 1.25rem 0px; font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">安装:</span></strong></h4><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">sudo&nbsp;apt-get&nbsp;install&nbsp;python-virtualenv\r\n或者\r\nsudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;virtualenv</pre><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Oxygen, Georgia, serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(82, 82, 82); margin: 1.25rem 0px; font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">使用方法:</strong></span></h4><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">virtualenv&nbsp;--no-site-packages&nbsp;[虚拟环境名称]&nbsp;\r\n#&nbsp;--no-site-packages&nbsp;参数可以不加，它的作用\r\n#&nbsp;是使虚拟环境不依赖系统环境中的site-packages</pre><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Oxygen, Georgia, serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(82, 82, 82); margin: 1.25rem 0px; font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">启动虚拟环境:</strong></span></h4><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">cd&nbsp;ENV\r\nsource&nbsp;./bin/activate</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">注意此时命令行会多一个<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">(ENV)</code>，ENV为虚拟环境名称，接下来所有模块都只会安装到该目录中去。</span></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Oxygen, Georgia, serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(82, 82, 82); margin: 1.25rem 0px; font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/lzjun567/note/blob/master/python/virtualenv.md#-3\" name=\"-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 133, 197); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></a><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">退出虚拟环境:</strong></span></h4><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">deactivate</pre><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Oxygen, Georgia, serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(82, 82, 82); margin: 1.25rem 0px; font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">在虚拟环境安装Python套件:</strong></span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; vertical-align: baseline;\">Virtualenv 附带有pip安装工具，因此需要安装的套件可以直接运行：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;[套件名称]</pre>','2016-10-27 19:09:28.471990',0,1,1),
	(22,'mac下安装ipython失败的解决办法','<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在Mac上安装ipython的时候可能会遇到没有权限的问题，即使加了sudo也不可以，原因是Mac的新系统中加了SIP机制的原因，解决办法是：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">sudo&nbsp;pip&nbsp;install&nbsp;-U&nbsp;--user&nbsp;--force&nbsp;ipython</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">执行上述命令之后，即可安装ipython，但是安装之后在终端里执行ipython会提醒</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">-bash: ipython: command not found</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是在终端里执行</p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">python&nbsp;-m&nbsp;IPython</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">就可以进入ipython，为了以后使用方便，可以将以下代码加入到.bash_profile(在家目录下，没有自建)：</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">alias&nbsp;ipython=&#39;python&nbsp;-m&nbsp;IPython&#39;</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最后执行</span></p><pre class=\"brush:python;toolbar:false\">source&nbsp;~/.bash_profile</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使修改立即生效即可</span></p>','2018-05-11 19:13:37.040740',0,1,13);

